  "notes": "Haxby et al. 2001 (OpenNeuro ds000105) 8-way object category classifier; minimally preprocessed (motion correction + rigid coregistration to run 1 + linear detrending via FSL, see tutorial/preprocess_haxby.sh) -- not a scientifically rigorous preprocessing pipeline",
